'''Patna Book Fair''' or ''Patna Pushtak Mela'' is an annual book fair organized in [[Patna]], India by the Centre for Readership Development (CRD), an NGO, held annually (usually in the middle of November) at the [[Gandhi Maidan]],<ref name="indiatimes1">{{cite web|author=|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/patna/Book-fair-back-at-original-venue/articleshow/256087.cms?referral=PM |title=Book fair back at original venue - The Times of India |publisher=Timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=2003-10-29 |accessdate=2014-05-01}}</ref> selling and exhibiting books, printed matter, [[stationery]], [[printing]], [[compact discs]] and other [[multimedia]] publishing.<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/patna/Patna-book-fair-witnesses-over-1-lakh-visitors-on-last-day/articleshow/10794744.cms?referral=PM |title=Patna book fair witnesses over 1 lakh visitors on last day - The Times of India |publisher=Timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=2011-11-19 |accessdate=2014-05-01}}</ref><ref name="intoday1"/>
The First Patna Book Fair was held in 1985<ref name="intoday1"/> and November 2013 was its 20th edition.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.patnadaily.com/index.php/news/9033-patna-book-fair-just-hours-away-from-opening.html |title=Patna Book Fair Just Hours away from Opening |publisher=PatnaDaily.Com |date= |accessdate=2014-05-01}}</ref> During 1999-2002 the venue was shifted to Patliputra colony grounds.<ref name="indiatimes1"/> Next book fair<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.timesofindia.com/city/patna/patna-book-fair-from-feb-4/articleshow/56693574.cms |title=Patna book fair from Feb 4 |publisher=TimesOfIndia.com |date= |accessdate=2017-01-23}}</ref> is going to be organised on 4 February 2017 at Gandhi Maidan. The date was shifted from November due to [[350th Prakash Parv]].

Representatives from book publishing and multimedia companies from all over India and Foreign publishers from USA, UK, and Singapore come to the Fair.<ref name="intoday1"/> The November 2013 book fair had a total of 1000 stalls,<ref>{{cite web|author=Our Correspondent |url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1131019/jsp/bihar/story_17467452.jsp#.U2KJ8IGDkTA |title=More than books at fair |publisher=Telegraphindia.com |date=2013-10-19 |accessdate=2014-05-01}}</ref> covering around 2.5 lakh square feet area.<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/patna/Patna-book-fair-from-November-10/articleshow/24356604.cms |title=Patna book fair from November 10 - The Times of India |publisher=Timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=2013-10-19 |accessdate=2014-05-01}}</ref>

